Introduction

82MAJOR (formerly known as RARE HOUSE) is a six-member boy group under Great M Entertainment. They debuted on October 11, 2023, with the single album "ON."

The name "82MAJOR" combines the number "82", Korea's international calling code, and the word "MAJOR," reflecting the group's aspiration to become a major K-pop act.

The members of 82MAJOR are Seongil, Yechan, Seongmo, Seongbin, Seokjoon, and Dogyun.

The name of the fandom '82DE' is a portmanteau of "attitude," meaning to always be with a heartfelt and sincere attitude towards each other.
